[center][b]16. ھەقىقى بىلىم، ئادەمگە قاناق بېرىدۇ[/b][/center]  
[b]English:[/b] True knowledge gives life to the soul.  
[b]Explanation:[/b] Learning enriches our inner self, not just our minds.

[center][b]17. كۈندىلىك ئۇقۇش، كۈندىلىك ئۆسۈش[/b][/center]  
[b]English:[/b] Daily learning is daily growth.  
[b]Explanation:[/b] Intellectual growth is a process, not a destination.

[center][b]18. ئالدى بىلەن ئاڭلاش، كېيىن گەپ قىلىش[/b][/center]  
[b]English:[/b] Listen first, then speak.  
[b]Explanation:[/b] Thoughtful communication begins with understanding others.

[center][b]19. ئەقىللىق پەقەت جاۋاب ئەمەس، سوئالمۇ بىلىدۇ[/b][/center]  
[b]English:[/b] A wise man not only answers but asks.  
[b]Explanation:[/b] The ability to ask good questions is as important as answering.

[center][b]20. سۆز ئۆلچەنگەن بولسۇن[/b][/center]  
[b]English:[/b] Words must be measured.  
[b]Explanation:[/b] Speak thoughtfully and responsibly; words carry power.

